        <abstract> 
<p>In answer to CD’s query, FM thinks the seeds he sent were those of the sensitive <hi rend="italic">Mimosa</hi>.</p>  
<p>Reports his observations of movement of leaves of <hi rend="italic">Bauhinia grandiflora</hi> and <hi rend="italic">B. brasiliensis</hi>. They do not "sleep" in hot weather.</p>  
<p>Sends some seeds of <hi rend="italic">Pontederia</hi> he had fertilised.</p> 
        </abstract>
